summary: The document is a segment of the records disclosed under the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992, originating from the CIA. It features a handwritten list labeled 'ASSETS KNOWN', with a placeholder date of 01/01/1900. This unclassified document was partially released to the public, with certain sections redacted, and was last reviewed on 12/01/97. The document includes various handwritten notes and lists, some of which are difficult to decipher.
key_findings: Document pertains to the JFK assassination records.
Includes a handwritten list titled 'ASSETS KNOWN'.
Disclosed under the JFK Assassination Records Act of 1992, with portions redacted.
The document is unclassified and has been partially made available to the public.
